<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Fri, 18 Mar 2022 06:48:24 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>Deepfake 影片換臉假冒烏克蘭投降，澤連斯基 IG 親拍片澄清闢謠</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/03/18/deepfakesurrender/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=deepfakesurrender</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[samuel]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 18 Mar 2022 06:48:24 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[Deepfake]]></category><category><![CDATA[instagram]]></category><category><![CDATA[Twitter]]></category><category><![CDATA[澤連斯基]]></category><category><![CDATA[烏克蘭]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1091405</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>近日在 Twitter 上流傳一段使用 Deepfake 技術假冒烏克蘭總統宣佈投降的偽造影片，而澤連斯基隨後 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>近日在 Twitter 上流傳一段使用 Deepfake 技術假冒烏克蘭總統宣佈投降的偽造影片，而澤連斯基隨後亦親身拍片回應闢謠。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1091407" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/澤連斯基-502x580.jpg" alt="" width="502" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/澤連斯基-502x580.jpg 502w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/澤連斯基.jpg 556w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 502px" /></p><p>影片中，偽冒的澤連斯基站在講臺後發言，內容大意指戰爭令他明白到當總統並非易事，自己的軍隊在戰爭中失敗了，決定將烏克蘭東部的頓巴斯歸還俄羅斯。影片結尾呼籲軍人放下武器，回到家人身邊，這場戰爭並不值得大家犧牲性命。目前該偽造影片已因違反 Twitter 規則而被移除。</p><p>Deepfake 技術透過移花接木，將人物頭像拼貼到影片或圖片中的身體上，以在視覺及聽覺矇騙他人。</p><p>流傳的影片充滿瑕疵，澤連斯基的頭部與人物軀幹連接得十分突兀，頭部過大而身軀太小；燈光照射角度並不自然，拍攝角度亦非常奇怪。一名來自英國 Sky News 新聞頻道的翻譯表示假冒澤連斯基的聲線比起真身更低沉、更慢。</p><p>而隨後澤連斯基在自己的官方 Instagram 上傳一段自拍影片，配以「我們在家保衛烏克蘭」的文字敘述以闢謠。</p><p>影片中澤連斯基說自己只會建議俄軍放下武器投降，自己與國民的確已回到家中，正為保衛土地、孩子、家庭而戰，在勝利之前絕不放下武器。</p><p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CbKYM_Zg2jo/">https://www.instagram.com/p/CbKYM_Zg2jo/</a></p><blockquote class="instagram-media" style="background: #FFF; border: 0; border-radius: 3px; margin: 1px; max-width: 540px; min-width: 326px; padding: 0; width: calc(100% - 2px);" data-instgrm-captioned="" data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/tv/CbKYM_Zg2jo/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14"><div style="padding: 16px;"><div style="flex-direction: row; align-items: center;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="height: 50px; margin: 0 auto 12px; width: 50px;"></div><div style="padding-top: 8px;"><div style="color: #3897f0; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 550; line-height: 18px;">在 Instagram 查看這則帖子</div></div><div style="padding: 12.5% 0;"></div><div style="flex-direction: row; margin-bottom: 14px; align-items: center;"><div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; height: 12.5px; width: 12.5px;"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; height: 12.5px; width: 12.5px; flex-grow: 0; margin-right: 14px; margin-left: 2px;"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; height: 12.5px; width: 12.5px;"></div></div><div style="margin-left: 8px;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 20px; width: 20px;"></div><div style="width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 2px solid transparent; border-left: 6px solid #f4f4f4; border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;"></div></div><div style="margin-left: auto;"><div style="width: 0px; border-top: 8px solid #F4F4F4; border-right: 8px solid transparent;"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; flex-grow: 0; height: 12px; width: 16px;"></div><div style="width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 8px solid #F4F4F4; border-left: 8px solid transparent;"></div></div></div><div style="flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 24px;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 224px;"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 144px;"></div></div><p style="color: #c9c8cd; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px; margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 8px; overflow: hidden; padding: 8px 0 7px; text-align: center;"><a style="color: #c9c8cd; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 17px; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.instagram.com/tv/CbKYM_Zg2jo/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Володимир Зеленський（@zelenskiy_official）分享的帖子</a></p></div></blockquote><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CbKYM_Zg2jo/">澤連斯基 Instagram</a> &amp; <a href="https://news.sky.com/story/ukraine-war-deepfake-video-of-zelenskyy-telling-ukrainians-to-lay-down-arms-debunked-12567789">Sky News</a></p><p><span lang="EN-US">unwire.hk Mewe </span>專頁<span lang="EN-US"> : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</a></span></p></p><div class="feedflare">
