</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>METAL BUILD GUNDAM DEVISE EXIA     原型 GN 閃耀巨劍 + GN DEVISE 揹包</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/03/18/gundam-00-revealed-chronicle/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=gundam-00-revealed-chronicle</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Harold]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 18 Mar 2022 03:07:34 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[玩具]]></category><category><![CDATA[METAL BUILD《機動戰士 GUNDAM 00 REVEALED CHRONICLE》GUNDAM DEVISE EXIA]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1091231</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>「機動戰士高達 00」×「METAL BUILD」的新企劃「機動戰士高達 00 REVEALED CHRONI [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>「機動戰士高達 00」×「METAL BUILD」的新企劃「機動戰士高達 00 REVEALED CHRONICLE」，「Gundam Devise Exia」預計 2022 年 10 月推出。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1091259 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/mb00-694x387.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="387" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/mb00-694x387.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/mb00-768x429.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/mb00.jpg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>DEVISE 試驗型能天使高達配備了新裝備 GN Devise Backpack 及原型 GN 閃耀巨劍。背部的新裝備 GN Devise Backpack，藉由直列連接兩具太陽爐獲得更高性能，不過由於處於試驗階段所以僅安裝 GN 粒子儲藏槽。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1091276 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-17-at-9.49.33-PM-405x580.png" alt="" width="405" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-17-at-9.49.33-PM-405x580.png 405w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-17-at-9.49.33-PM-628x900.png 628w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-17-at-9.49.33-PM-768x1101.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-17-at-9.49.33-PM.png 936w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 405px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1091277 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-17-at-9.49.21-PM-694x480.png" alt="" width="694" height="480" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-17-at-9.49.21-PM-694x480.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-17-at-9.49.21-PM-1280x885.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-17-at-9.49.21-PM-768x531.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-17-at-9.49.21-PM.png 1348w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1091278 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-17-at-9.48.42-PM-694x578.png" alt="" width="694" height="578" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-17-at-9.48.42-PM-694x578.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-17-at-9.48.42-PM-1081x900.png 1081w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-17-at-9.48.42-PM-768x640.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-17-at-9.48.42-PM.png 1304w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1091279 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-17-at-9.48.34-PM-667x580.png" alt="" width="667" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-17-at-9.48.34-PM-667x580.png 667w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-17-at-9.48.34-PM-1034x900.png 1034w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-17-at-9.48.34